{"tid":1763387,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【3年抱3？】郭富城恨追仔 傳贈現金100萬利誘老婆再生","createTime":"2019-11-30T09:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T10:55:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"685c207c79942abc3ba322b503318d1c05e16ad3","tid":1763387,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"現年54歲的天王郭富城，2017年與比他年輕22歲的網紅方媛(Moka)結婚，隨後順利誕下女兒Chantelle，今年5月再生下小女兒Charlotte。巧合地，昔日的四大天王張學友、劉德華、黎明和郭富城全部都是生女，被網民稱為「四大父王」。<br />\n方媛今年只有32歲，不算是高齡產婦，一直盛傳城城好希望嫩妻能為自己追個仔，多次被傳媒追問，城城都輕鬆答「仔女都冇所謂」，並揚言不再生。不過，今日有台灣傳媒爆料，指城城最近心思思想追仔，為令年事已高的郭媽媽開心。<br />\n不過，生仔都要雙方配合，有指方媛曾跟閨密透露，城城最近出手好闊綽，以前從未送超過10萬港元的手袋，最近卻豪氣送贈約值12萬港元的Herm&egrave;s手袋，並氹老婆若囝囝出世後，會再送100萬港元現金做獎勵。但由於再生都未必是仔，有指二人特別去做健康檢查，亦有傳他們向閨密頻頻打聽生仔偏方，看看能否「一擊即中」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575090346_2558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575090346_2558.jpg&h=a5cb818d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191130/60327169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60327169&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=8b8ba450\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60327169&h=e566a2c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191130/60327169</a>"},{"pid":"d8f7482aed213fffed611a2c1a6f0a904e4b9004","tid":1763387,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"我打折50萬幫佢生得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6007e44738574dec3020cd3849e194cda41cf09a","tid":1763387,"uid":62815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTim